You do not finish a topic and discard it. You **layer**: a 2500 still solves tactics daily — they just solve harder ones, faster. The pyramid below is the proportion of study time by level.

```
                        2500-2800   [ Openings | Prep | Calc | Endgames | Fitness ]
                    2100-2300   [ Calculation | Strategy | Openings | Endgames ]
