## A realistic word on timelines

Each 200-point band typically takes **hundreds to thousands of hours** of focused work, and the bands get **exponentially** harder — going 2500→2700 is a different universe of effort than 1500→1700, and reaching the very top also requires talent, youth, coaching and time that not everyone has. This guide gives you the **correct map and methods**; how far you travel depends on the work you put in. The good news: the methods that make a 1500 into a 2000 are the same *kind* of methods that make a 2300 into a GM — just applied deeper. Climb one band at a time.

